title: IEV Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of the iShares Europe ETF (Symbol: IEV) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $42.54, changing hands as high as $42.60 per share. iShares Europe shares are currently trading up about 1.1% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of IEV shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, IEV's low point in its 52 week range is $37.75 per share, with $46.08 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $42.57.
